jflowmap.bundling

Class ForceDirectedEdgeBundler

  • java.lang.Object
    • jflowmap.bundling.ForceDirectedEdgeBundler

  • public class ForceDirectedEdgeBundler
extends java.lang.Object
    This is an implementation of the algorithm described in the paper "Force-Directed Edge Bundling for Graph Visualization" by Danny Holten and Jarke J. van Wijk.
    Author:
    Ilya Boyandin
